  "!!!! A lire avant d'utiliser les \u00e9crans !!!!": {
   "width": 11940,
   "height": 2100,
   "color": "rgb(111,111,111)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "         Ces valeurs doivent \u00eatre saisies manuellement avant d'\u00eatre r\u00e9\u00e9crites.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 840,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 11040
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "- Le bouton \"REINITIALISATION\" permet d'\u00e9crire les valeurs d'initialisation d'un composant suite au changement de celui-ci. ",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 1200,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 11040
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "  Les valeurs seront automatiquement initialis\u00e9es lors de l'appui du bouton, aucune saisie n'est n\u00e9cessaire.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 1440,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 11040
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Dans les \u00e9crans suivants vous trouverez deux boutons: Ecriture et R\u00e9initialisation.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 360,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 11040
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "      - Apr\u00e8s une reprogrammation ou changement d'un calculateur le bouton \"ECRITURE\" permet de r\u00e9\u00e9crire les valeurs pr\u00e9c\u00e9demment sauvegard\u00e9es.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 600,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 11040
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    }
   ],
